INV annual PM completed. with details:

Kyle and Eric completed the annual PM on 6/02/2025. Kyle and Eric shut the inverter down by keying off, AUX switch off, AC/DC switch off, LBD switch off in the field, and switch gear cabinet C OFF/Grounded. Kyle and Eric cleaned the inverter throughout all the doors, checked for any damage and leaks. After Kyle and Eric completed the inspection and found no issues Kyle and Eric removed all the LOTO and proceeded to turn the inverter back on.
